_sText: This is a Fight Yard Map with many Glass Textures. At Map Spawn all Players have a Deagle and a Knife. I have put a Weapon Holder with 2 Shotguns and 2 AWP's. At the under middle sectore i have put 2 HE Grenades and 1 Deagle (maybe you have no Ammo then take this one). There are NAV Files into the Pack, so you can play with BOTS.
